unholygauntlet.name: Unholy Gauntlet
unholygauntlet.description:
The Unholy Gauntlet is an official FragMC map mainly built by one of our builders: Ninja.

This map incorperates all of the mechanics (as of writing) and amazing scenery. As well as this, it has multiple parts of deception involved with it and is by far one of the most scenic maps on FragMC.
